  #hosts-section
    .container-fluid
      .section-title
        h3 Get treated
        hr
        p When you’re on our guestlist, you’ll be taken care of by a host. Our hosts are vetted professionals who know the venues in and out. They'll make sure you breeze through the line take care of your every need.
            
  #invite-guests-section
    .container-fluid
      .section-title
        h3 Make it Hype
        p Parties are better with friends. The more people you bring with you to the party, the better your night gets. Not only do you get to enjoy experiences with your friends, you’ll get rewarded too.

  #beta-section
    .container
      .section-title
        h3 Coming soon to the app store
        hr
      .row-centered
        a.beta-access-button(href='/betarequest') REQUEST ACCESS TO THE BETA
  
